'''Ndjoli Kayitankore''' ni Umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye muri [[kongo]] iya 23, Ugushyingo 1962 i [[Goma]]<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/81641</ref><ref>https://www.webrwanda.com/2020/07/ubuzima-butangaje-bwa-kanyombya-mu.html</ref>. Wamenekanye cyane mu gukina filimi zo gusetsa mu [[Rwanda]] nka '''Kanyombya''' kuko yatangiye kuzikina 2001.<ref>https://www.inyenyerinews.org/justice-and-reconciliation/kayitankore-ndjoli-uzwi-nka-kanyombya-ari-mu-maboko-ya-polisi-azira-urugomo/</ref>byatumye amenyekana cyane kuko afatwa nkumwe mubantu bifatizo muri filimi zo gusetsa mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://impano.rw/ubuzima-bwa-kanyombwa-mu-gisirikare/</ref>. Yakinnye harimo "Bwenjye naguhenze,"Buhahara","abatubuzi","ibikuruka", "nyabingi" nizindi<ref>https://urwenya.wordpress.com/category/kanyombya/</ref><ref>https://www.urwego.com/2016/05/kanyombya-yatangaje-impamvu.html</ref>

== ubuzima bwa Kanyombya muri make ==
'''Kanyombya''' yavutse kuri mama we Gaudence Mukandutiye na papa we Jean Baptiste Sakumi, avukira mu muryango w'abana 7 gusa hasigaye 5<ref>http://imvahonshya.co.rw/umunyarwenya-kanyombya-yemeza-ko-ibyo-akora-bimutunze/</ref>. Yize amashuri abanza kuri ecole primaire ste Andre i [[Goma]], akomereza ayisumbuye muri Tuugane Institute ahava muri 1992 ahita ajya mu gisirikare yaje kuvamo muri 2002<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/sinigeze-mbyarana-na-kanyombya-nyinawambogo-yashyize-hanze-ukuri-video</ref><ref>http://isimbi.rw/sinema/article/ubundi-bukwe-bwanjye-buraje-kanyombya-video</ref>. Mu gisirikare yarwaniye mu ngabo za '''RPA''' zafashe igihugu  muri 1994 , Avuye mugisirikare nibwo yatangiye gukina filimi kugeza nanubu ntiyigeze ahagarara<ref>https://5kuri5.com/kanyombya-mu-nkotanyi-ubuzima-butangaje-mugisirikare-yamazemo-imyaka-10/</ref>. '''Kanyombya''' ubu afite umugore babanaga nuko baza gusezerana imbere y'amategeko muri 2012 kandi bafitanye abana 2 ndetse n'abandi barera<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/kanyombwa-yasinye-amasezerano-yo-kujya-yamamaza-kompanyi-ikomeye-yabanyaturukiyaamafoto/</ref>. '''Kanyombya''' avugako impano yo gusetsa yayikuye ku muryango we kuko ngo bose abazi basetsa haba abavandimwe n'ababyeyi be.<ref>https://bwiza.com/?kanyombya-ukina-filimi-ntazi-amazina-ya-minisitiri-w-039-umuco-na-siporo</ref><ref>https://www.igihe.com/newinsinema</ref>

